A new trailer has been unleashed for American thriller film &#8220;The Circle,&#8221; ahead of its scheduled debut in theatres this on April 28.The feature, based on the novel by Dave Eggers, stars British actress Emma Watson as Mae Holland, a young woman who lands a job at a powerful tech conglomerate and becomes embroiled in a mysterious web.Touching on topics of privacy, surveillance and pubic freedom, the story was brought to life by writer-director-producer James Ponsoldt, and features Tom Hanks in a rare villainous role, as the cult-like company&#8217;s founder.John Boyega, Karen Gillan, Patton Oswalt, and Ellar Coltrane round out the main cast.-Relaxnews